mil.emp3.api.interfaces

Interface IOverlay

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IContainer, IGeoBase, IGeoContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Overlay

    public interface IOverlay
extends IContainer, IGeoContainer
    This interface defines the the methods associated with an overlay.
